It is noteworthy that no new probable cases were reported in the past 24 hours
As of 18 Jun 2003 a cumulative total of 5326 probable cases with 347 deaths
have been reported. At present there are a total of 220 suspected cases
still pending in China.

These 22 provinces have not reported a new probable case in the past 20 or
more days: Hebei, Shanxi, Inner Mongolia, Shanghai, Hubei, Guangxi,
Guangdong, Tianjin, Jilin, Gansu,Jiangsu, Anhui, Shaanxi, Zhejiang, Henan,
Chongqing, Jiangxi, Ningxia, Shandong, Fujian, Hunan and Xinjiang..

