Active SARS cases in Canada
---------------------------
"Active" cases include those hospitalized, currently ill at home, or under
investigation.

Date: May: 28 / 29 / 30 / Jun: 2 / 3 / 4 / 5 / 6 / 9/ 10 / 11 / 12 / 13 /
16 / 17
Probable (active)
13 / 19 / 43 / 62 / 64 / 67 / 68 / 70 / 66 / 64 / 65 / 60 / 55 / 44 / 37
